OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a dry start rain will
OL,6,Fspread to the northwest this morning,
OL,7,Fbut dry and bright in the east. Then
OL,8,Fthis afternoon will be cloudy with
OL,9,Frain, but patchy in the east. Drier in
OL,10,Fthe far north later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will clear away south
OL,13,Fduring this evening. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will be dry with clear
OL,15,Fperiods and a few light showers. Cold
OL,16,Fwith a frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FIsolated showers at first
OL,19,Fotherwise a dry day with some bright
OL,20,For sunny spells. Cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
